Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
selectPin(25.10)                                              selectPin(25.10)

Name
       selectPin - Selects the specified pin

Syntax
       selectPin

        [-help]

       <name>

       Selects the specified pin.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description that includes type and default infor-
              mation for each selectPin parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man selectPin

       <name> Specifies the name of the pin to be selected.

Example
       The following example selects the swack pin.

       selectPin swack

Related Information
              * deselectPin

